provided that it doesnt fade as quickly as it blossomed some 
analysts believe the revived rally holds out a positive message for 
consumers workers and managers in many sectors of the economy 
they argue that the strength in the markets signals improved 
odds that the economic expansion dating from late 1982 still has 
some distance to run 
