defense secretary dick cheney proposed reducing the pentagons 
planned purchase of b2 stealth bombers c17 transport planes and 
other sophisticated aircraft 
cheneys action came in response to the lessening soviet threat 
and increasing congressional sentiment for a reduction in defense 
spending 
